    content: "Kash(❖,❖) | NPC LEADER [GRIT], Role icon, Ritualist — 31/07/2025 19:29\nGuess the Song: \nWhere Lyrics Confuse and Beats Betray 🎧\n\nYou know your music? Can spot a song from just one line, a weird clue, or three dramatic emojis? Welcome to Guess the Song, the game where your playlist loyalty is put to the ultimate test.\n\nWe’ll drop a trivia clue maybe a lyric, maybe a fun fact, maybe “That song where  Justine Bieber hums before he even says a word” and you have to name the track.\n\nEasy? Until you realize you’ve been confidently singing the wrong lyrics your whole life. (“It’s not ‘I got one less problem without you’?”)\n\nExpect intense debates, throwback confusion, someone yelling “I KNOW THIS!” while clearly not knowing it, and the thrill of finally guessing it right just before someone else does.\n\nYou gotta channel that inner Shazam, let’s find out who really runs the aux cord.\n\n@Events \n\nhttps://discord.com/events/1210468736205852672/1392884947731222558\nBATTLESHIP WAR\nBattleship War \n\nAlright commanders grab your maps, load your cannons,\nand prepare to turn the ocean into a war zone of chaos and screams!\n\nWe’re playing BATTLESHIP, the game where you don’t just attack - you destroy ships one missile at a time. The ultimate mind game where one lucky guess can make you a legend,\nand one wrong move can make you say “BRO, HOW?!”",
