    content: "Kash(❖,❖) | NPC LEADER [GRIT], Role icon, Ritualist — 08/10/2025 20:53\nLet’s puzzle people\nEvery Wednesday, the Ritual Puzzle Game takes over a global test of brains and patience. Also known as \n\n“the puzzle that makes you regret opening Discord,”\n\nit’s not for the faint hearted. The rules? Simple to read, painful to beat: whoever solves it first is either a genius or just has terrifying brainpower.\n\nLink: https://ritualpicpuzzle.vercel.app/\n\nHow to play:\n• Open the link on your laptop or phone.\n• Shuffle the puzzle.\n• First to finish wins the glory.\n\nGET READY FOR SOME RITUAL FUN \n\n@Events \nhttps://discord.com/events/1210468736205852672/1409952104033947840\nRitual Puzzle\nEvery Wednesday, the Naija voice channel transforms into a battleground of wits with the Ritual Puzzle Game also known as “the puzzle that makes you regret joining Discord.” \nThe rules? Simple on paper, painful in practice: whoever completes the puzzle first is either a certified genius or just has scary brain power\n\nThis isn’t your usual game, it’s a psychological experiment disguised as fun. Puzzles so hard it’ll make you doubt if you ever passed JSS2 Mathematics.\n\nHost: Ogumaterry\nCohost: Cookie\nRitual Puzzle - Picture Puzzle Game\nRitual Puzzle - A challenging sliding picture puzzle game for the Ritual Community. Test your skills and compete on the leaderboard!",
